channel.title: Where did i screw up with port forwarding?
channel.description: I checked my port and it said its open. I downloaded some port forwarding software to open it. but then when i open my source run.bat it says port already in use? so i exited out of the port forward software and re opened my run.bat and it worked but then when i started my port forward software it said port already in use.
